For those who find this exploration of containment and commutation… *fascinating*, there are related concepts. You might want to delve into the [Centralizer and normalizer](/Centralizer_and_normalizer), which describe sets of elements that commute or normalize specific subsets, rather than all elements. Or perhaps the [Center (category theory)](/Center_(category_theory)), a more abstract generalization of this idea in the realm of categories.

